name: Liquid Death Mountain Water 19.2oz
description:
Liquid Death's still water is 100% mountain water from the alps. They contain over 2x more electrolytes than other brands like Essentia, SmartWater, LifeWtr, Core, and Aquafina.

name: Liquid Death Sparkling Water 19.2oz
description:
Liquid Death Sparkling Water doesn’t just look like a beer, it is actually carbonated like a beer. We use a more drinkable level of carbonation (5 grams/L) more similar to most beers than the higher carbonation levels of most sodas (6-8 grams/L). Slightly less carbonation means less carbonic acid is formed, which means the taste of Liquid Death is less bitter and more thirst murderous than many other sparkling waters. But most importantly, we made sure there is still plenty of carbonation for award-winning belches.

name: Elite Naturel Cold Pressed Organic Fresh Green Smoothie - 330 ml Bottle
description:
Fresh smoothie customers can grab & go!

Elite Natural Fresh Green Smoothie is produced with organic fruits and vegetables that come entirely from our own fields. Fruits and vegetables collected in the season are subjected to chemical residue analysis and then filled into bottles by cold pressing method. Fresh Green Smoothie, which passes through flash pasteurization, reaches you, our valuable consumers, without losing its vitamins and minerals.

INGREDIENTS:
Cucumber Juice*, Spinach Juice*, Green Apple Puree , Lime Juice*, Parsley Juice*, Dill Juice*.  *ORGANIC
